Name: Fighters Unleashed
About the game: Battle your way through waves of zombies, military commands, gangs without heart, ninjas skilled and ruthless mobsters. Take the role of Alexia or Charlie, two people with special abilities, on a mission to rescue Megan, who has been kidnapped for unknown reasons. To rescue Megan you must use unique moves, and special combinations, motorcycles, super powers, and more. Unleash the fighter in you with incredible martial skills and mysterious powers you'll discover in your amazing adventure Discover how to defeat each of their powerful bosses, and develops the Charlie and Alexia skills as you go and get experience.
